Class RestartCase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.analysis.GenericObject
      • com.cafean.client.analysis.AbstractComponent

          • com.cafean.client.analysis.RestartCase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Checkable, ComponentElement, IdentHolder, ModelElement, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractIntegrationCase
    public abstract class RestartCase
extends AbstractBeanComponent
    This class represents a derivative case on an AbstractModel. What this means is heavily plug-in dependent, but generally it supports providing one or more situations for restarting the primary model.
